<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN295">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>kaṭalkiḷarn taṉṉa kaṭṭūr nāppaṇ</l>
<l>vēntuvāy maṭittu  vēṟalaip peyarit</l>
<l>tōṭukait teḻutarūu turanteṟi ñāṭpiṉ</l>
<l>varupaṭai pōḻntu vāyppaṭa vilaṅki</l>
<l>yiṭaippaṭai yaḻuvattuc citaintuvē ṟākiya</l>
<l>ciṟappuṭai yāḷaṉ māṇpukaṇ ṭaruḷi</l>
<l>vāṭumulai yūṟic curantaṉa</l>
<l>vōṭāp pūṭkai viṭalai tāykkē</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>In the middle of the war camp that shines up like the sea,</l>
<l>when the king, pursing [his] mouth, turning the tip of [his] spear,</l>
<l>moving the multitude moving, rising, driving on, cutting </l>
<l>into the army that came with attacking weapons, found a way,</l>
<l>the excellent man who while blocking was destroyed in the thicker of the middle army</l>
<l>[and] become another, upon seeing his glory, graciously</l>
<l>the withered breasts dripped [and] gave [milk] abundantly,</l>
<l>of the mother of the bull with the resolution not to flee.   </l>
</lg>
    </div>
